  "title": "Senior QC Lab Equipment Qualification Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: QC Lab Equipment Qualification Engineer - Contracted</p><p>Job Description:</p><ul><li>Manage QC Lab equipment qualification projects as per change control and validation processes.</li><li>Manage decommissioning of QC Lab equipment.</li><li>Define qualification project strategy and timeline.</li><li>Support deviations, CAPA and change control arising from lab equipment qualification.</li><li>Lead and execute IQ/OQ/PQ activities, while ensuring effective collaboration and communication across all stakeholders.</li><li>Monitor project progress, identifying and addressing any issues or risks that may arise.</li><li>Ensure that all project activities comply with regulatory requirements, industry standards, and Client’s quality assurance protocols.</li><li>Manage project documentation, including contracts, permits, and technical specifications.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Minimum 2-4 years' experience in qualification of QC Lab equipment in life science industry</li><li>Diploma/Degree in engineering</li><li>Candidate must be willing to accept a 1-year contract role with likelihood of extension</li></ul>",
